---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section id="work" className="my-10 w-full">
  <div class="bg-gray-100 py-36">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-2xl gap-10 px-10">
      <div class="w-[60%]">
        <h2 class="font-audiowide text-3xl font-semibold uppercase">
          What I can do
        </h2>

        <h3 class="pt-5 text-black/70">Like I said, you name it. I give it.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 text-3xl">
        <p>Figma designs</p>
        <p>Scalable Architectures</p>
        <p>Backend Development</p>
        <p>Frontend Development</p>
        <p>Search Engine Optimization</p>
        <p>Mail Campaigns + Landing Pages</p>
        <p>Chrome Extensions</p>
        <p>Birthday Sites</p>
        <p>Wedding Sites</p>
        <p>E Commerce</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-2xl gap-10 px-10 py-36">
    <div class="flex w-[60%] flex-col justify-between">
      <h2 class="font-audiowide text-3xl font-semibold uppercase">
        What my friends can do
      </h2>

      <div class="">
        <p class="pt-5 text-black/70">
          I said, you name it. I give it. Which is sometimes wrong.
        </p>
        <p class="pt-5 text-black/70">Instead, you name it. we give it.</p>
        <p class="max-w-[55%] pt-5 font-medium">
          Throughout the years of collaborating with clients, I've built a
          network of high-performance individuals ready to help us if needed.
        </p>
        <p class="max-w-[55%] pt-5 font-medium">
          Once we start working together, I can intro you, or I can arrange the
          entire collaboration myself, so that you won't have to lift a finger.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 text-3xl">
      <p>Pretty much everything that I do, and</p>
      <p>IOS Apps</p>
      <p>Mobile Apps</p>
      <p>PWA, etc</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

